<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Sequence on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sequence/</link><description>Recent content in Sequence on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/sequence/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] F# InvalidOperation Sequence Is Empty</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-invalidoperation-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-invalidoperation-v2/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;InvalidOperationException&lt;/code&gt; with message &lt;code&gt;Sequence contains no elements&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you call &lt;code&gt;Seq.head&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Seq.first&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;Seq.exactlyOne&lt;/code&gt;, or similar functions on an empty sequence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling head/first on empty collection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using single where multiple elements exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;LINQ First() without Where predicate matching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Empty result from database query&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Calling head on empty sequence
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; items&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; int &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;list&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; first &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; List.head items &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// InvalidOperationException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Check if empty first
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; items&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; int &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;list&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; first &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; List.isEmpty items &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt; 0 &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; List.head items
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Seq.head on empty
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Seq.head &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Seq.empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use Seq.tryHead (F# 6+)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Seq.tryHead &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Seq.empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// result = None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: LINQ First() on empty
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;open&lt;/span&gt; System.Linq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; items &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Seq.empty&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; first &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; items&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;First() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// InvalidOperationException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use Seq.tryHead or Seq.head with guard
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; first &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; Seq.isEmpty items &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;then&lt;/span&gt; 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; Seq.head items
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe head functions
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; safeHead xs &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; xs &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; [] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; None
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; Some x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Seq.tryHead (F# 6+)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; items &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; List.toSeq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; first &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; items &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; Seq.tryHead &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Some 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Default value with headOr
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; headOr defaultVal xs &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; xs &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; [] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; defaultVal
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; headOr 0 [] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; result2 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; headOr 0 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-indexoutofrange/"&gt;fsharp-indexoutofrange&lt;/a&gt; — index out of range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-notfoundexception/"&gt;fsharp-notfoundexception&lt;/a&gt; — key not found&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-matcherror/"&gt;fsharp-matcherror&lt;/a&gt; — match failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python IndexError — List Index Out of Range</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/index-out-of-range/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/index-out-of-range/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="indexerror--list-index-out-of-range"&gt;IndexError — List Index Out of Range&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;IndexError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;list index out of range&amp;rdquo; is raised when you try to access an index that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist in a list. The index is either too large, too negative, or the list is empty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Python lists are zero-indexed. A list of length &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; has valid indices from &lt;code&gt;0&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;n-1&lt;/code&gt;. Accessing any index outside this range raises an &lt;code&gt;IndexError&lt;/code&gt;. This error is common with off-by-one mistakes, empty lists, and stale indices after list modification.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python IndexError — Tuple Index Out of Range</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/tuple-index/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/tuple-index/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="indexerror--tuple-index-out-of-range"&gt;IndexError — Tuple Index Out of Range&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;IndexError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;tuple index out of range&amp;rdquo; is raised when you try to access an index that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist in a tuple. Like lists, tuples are zero-indexed, and accessing an invalid index raises an error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tuples are immutable sequences in Python. They are zero-indexed just like lists. A tuple of length &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; has valid indices from &lt;code&gt;0&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;n-1&lt;/code&gt;. Accessing any index outside this range raises &lt;code&gt;IndexError&lt;/code&gt;. The key difference from lists is that tuples cannot be modified after creation.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Python ValueError — Not Enough Values to Unpack</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/unpack-non-sequence/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/python/unpack-non-sequence/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="valueerror--not-enough-values-to-unpack"&gt;ValueError — Not Enough Values to Unpack&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ValueError&lt;/code&gt; with the message &amp;ldquo;not enough values to unpack&amp;rdquo; is raised when you try to unpack a sequence into more variables than the sequence contains. The number of variables must match the number of elements, or you must use starred expressions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sequence unpacking assigns elements of a sequence to variables. Python requires the number of variables to match the number of elements, unless you use &lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt; to capture remaining elements. This error is common when data has unexpected length.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>InvalidOperationException in F#</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-invalidoperation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-invalidoperation/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;InvalidOperationException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when a method call is invalid given the object&amp;rsquo;s current state. This commonly happens with sequence enumeration and collection operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modifying collection during enumeration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calling method on disposed object&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using enumerator after collection changed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invalid state transition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Handle sequence modification:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; numbers &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 2&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 4&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; 5&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong: modifying during enumeration
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// for n in numbers do
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// if n = 3 then numbers.Remove(n)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct: create new collection
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; filtered &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; numbers &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; List.filter &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use.toList before modification:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle - ORA-08004: sequence exceeds MAXVALUE</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-sequence-error-v2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-sequence-error-v2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;ORA-08004: sequence exceeds MAXVALUE occurs when a sequence has reached its defined maximum value and cannot generate a new number. This typically happens with sequences that have CYCLE disabled or when the MAXVALUE is too small for the workload.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence MAXVALUE reached&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NOCYCLE option set on the sequence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MAXVALUE set too low during creation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Large batch inserts consuming sequence values rapidly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence not configured with sufficient range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check current sequence value:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; sequence_name, last_number, max_value, increment_by
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; user_sequences
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; sequence_name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;MY_SEQ&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Alter the sequence to increase MAXVALUE:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;999999999&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reset the sequence value:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; my_seq.NEXTVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- adjust current value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recreate sequence with higher MAXVALUE:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;START&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WITH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;9999999999&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; NOCYCLE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CACHE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use CYCLE option for sequences that should wrap around:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CYCLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;999999&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="6"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use identity columns (Oracle 12c+):&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; users (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; id NUMBER &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;GENERATED&lt;/span&gt; ALWAYS &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IDENTITY&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;START&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WITH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; name VARCHAR2(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: ORA-08004: sequence MY_SEQ exceeds MAXVALUE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; my_seq.NEXTVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ORA-08004: sequence MY_SEQ exceeds MAXVALUE and cannot be instantiated
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: increase MAXVALUE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE my_seq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;99999999&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; my_seq.NEXTVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- 10001
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-trigger-error/"&gt;Trigger error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error/"&gt;Tablespace error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Oracle Sequence Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-sequence-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-sequence-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="oracle-sequence-error"&gt;Oracle Sequence Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An Oracle sequence error occurs when a sequence fails to generate the next value. Sequences are used for auto-incrementing primary keys in Oracle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence exhausted (reached MAXVALUE)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence cache issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequence does not exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ORDER/NOCORDER mismatch in RAC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-sequence-status"&gt;Check Sequence Status&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; sequence_name, last_number, increment_by, max_value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; user_sequences;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="get-next-value"&gt;Get Next Value&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; myseq.NEXTVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="reset-sequence"&gt;Reset Sequence&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; myseq.NEXTVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Go back
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="create-new-sequence"&gt;Create New Sequence&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;START&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WITH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INCREMENT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;BY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; NOCACHE
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; NOCYCLE;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-cache-issues"&gt;Fix Cache Issues&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CACHE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="handle-maxvalue"&gt;Handle MAXVALUE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Check current value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; myseq.CURRVAL &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; dual;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Reset if exhausted
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RESTART&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;START&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WITH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (myseq.NEXTVAL, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ORA&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;08004&lt;/span&gt;: sequence MYSEQ.NEXTVAL exceeds &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix: alter sequence
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; SEQUENCE myseq &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;MAXVALUE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;999999999&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;Constraint Error&lt;/a&gt; — unique constraint violation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/oracle/oracle-tablespace-error/"&gt;Tablespace Error&lt;/a&gt; — tablespace issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>